&lt;h4&gt;Passive Information gathering&lt;span class=&#34;hx:absolute hx:-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;passive-information-gathering&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#passive-information-gathering&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As part of passive information gathering, we can use the OSINT tools to gather information from a web application.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:flex-col hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-4 hx:px-4 hx:border-gray-200 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-blue-200 hx:bg-blue-100 hx:text-blue-900 hx:dark:border-blue-200/30 hx:dark:bg-blue-900/30 hx:dark:text-blue-200&#34;&gt;
